    "All data were collected and presented anonymously, ensuring participant confidentiality throughout the study and beyond.",
    "ResultsA total of 512 researchers were invited to participate in the study through the aforementioned communication tools.",
    "Data was collected between June and August 2023.",
    "Of those invited, 320 agreed to participate, resulting in a response rate Factors Influencing ChatGPT and Chatbot UtilizationTable 4 presents findings from univariate analyses investigating factors related to the use of ChatGPT and other chatbots by the participants.",
    "A prominent revelation is the markedly higher inclination towards these tools among younger researchers."
